# ğŸ”¢ Advanced Number Manipulation

A JavaScript mini application that performs **conditional logic operations** on two numbers based on their signs.

## ğŸ“Œ Description
The user enters two numbers **A** and **B**.  
When clicking the button, the program checks their signs and applies one of two operations:

- **If A and B have the same sign (or one is zero):**
  - Their values are swapped
- **If A and B have different signs:**
  - A becomes the sum of A and B
  - B becomes the product of the original values

The new values are then displayed on the screen.

